      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Silver Grey Metallic. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline via six individual throttle bodies. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory variable M differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe and a serviced VANOS system to ensure valve timing precision. The chassis remains taut with upgraded polyurethane bushings and refreshed dampers, maintaining the communicative steering rack's feedback. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain remains robust and the rod bearings have been proactive-serviced. A purist-spec enthusiast machine ready for the canyon roads.",
